  • Constructor Details

    • Customer

      public Customer(int customerId, String customerName, String address, String postalCode, String phone, Timestamp createdDate, String createdBy, Timestamp lastUpdate, String lastUpdatedBy, int divisionId)
      Constructor class to create a Customer object represented in the Database. Note that Database is set to UTC time.
      Parameters:
      customerId - id of the customer (primary key)
      customerName - name of the customer
      address - address of the customer
      postalCode - postal code (or zip code) of the address
      phone - phone number of the customer
      createdDate - timestamp when the customer is created
      createdBy - the user who created the customer
      lastUpdate - timestamp when the customer was last updated
      lastUpdatedBy - the user who last updated the customer
      divisionId - location division where the customer belongs (foreign key)
